com.mobixell.xtt.gui.mapping
Class XttMapping

java.lang.Object
  com.mobixell.xtt.gui.mapping.XttMapping

public class XttMapping
extends Object

Mapping Jsystem GUI

Author:
Yaron This class is used a GUI mapping reader tool. it reads properties from the JSystemMappingProperties. the properties are used by the other clases to work with the TAS GUI objects when one of the GUI objects are changed, the only change that is needed is in the file
